                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Italian Colonies</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council considered document <gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M.(46)</gloss>
                        221<note n="43" xml:id="d277fn43">See <ref target="#pg_899">p. 899</ref>
                    </note> on the Italian Colonies.</p>
                <p>The English text of this document was adopted.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Germany</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Views were exchanged on the problem of Germany.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Austria</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Views were exchanged on the problem of Austria.</p>
                <pb facs="0941" n="917" xml:id="pg_917"/>
                <p rend="flushleft">IV. <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Friday, July 12, at 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>Agenda—Continuation of the discussion on Austria.</p>
